## âœ… Summary of URLs

| Service      | Default Port | Access URL             |
| ------------ | ------------ | ---------------------- |
| Prometheus   | `9090`       | `http://<EC2-IP>:9090` |
| Grafana      | `3000`       | `http://<EC2-IP>:3000` |
| Alertmanager | `9093`       | `http://<EC2-IP>:9093` |

